 contenir codi que aniria millor al giny de ÂŤHTML personalitzatÂť. Si no ho heu fet encara, quĂ¨ tal si el proveu?','%1$s &lsaquo; %2$s &#8212; WordPress'=>'%1$s &lsaquo; %2$s &#8212; WordPress','User action confirmed.'=>'S\'ha confirmat l\'acciĂł de l\'usuari.','Item added.'=>'S\'ha afegit l\'element.','Order'=>'Ordre','Embeds'=>'Incrustats','block titleEmbed'=>'Incrusta','Copy URL'=>'Copia l\'URL','Create'=>'Crea','Usage of the title attribute on the login logo is not recommended for accessibility reasons. Use the link text instead.'=>'No es recomana l\'Ăşs de l\'atribut ÂŤtitleÂť al logotip d\'inici de sessiĂł per motius d\'accessibilitat. Utilitzeu el text de l\'enllaĂ§ en el seu lloc.','Missing request ID.'=>'Falta l\'identificador de solÂˇlicitud.','Missing confirm key.'=>'Falta la clau de confirmaciĂł.','Recovery Mode Initialized. Please log in to continue.'=>'S\'ha inicialitzat el mode de recuperaciĂł. Inicieu sessiĂł per continuar.','Custom Colors'=>'Colors personalitzats','Recovery Mode &#8212; %s'=>'Mode recuperaciĂł &#8212; %s','Confirm your administration email'=>'Confirmeu el correu electrĂ˛nic d\'administraciĂł','Administration email verification'=>'VerificaciĂł del correu electrĂ˛nic d\'administraciĂł','Please verify that the <strong>administration email</strong> for this website is still correct.'=>'Verifiqueu que el <strong>correu electrĂ˛nic d\'administraciĂł</strong> d\'aquesta web ĂŠs encara correcte.','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/settings-general-screen/#email-address'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/settings-general-screen/#email-address','Why is this important?'=>'Per quĂ¨ ĂŠs aixĂ˛ important?','Current administration email: %s'=>'Actual correu electrĂ˛nic d\'administraciĂł: %s','This email may be different from your personal email address.'=>'Aquest correu electrĂ˛nic pot ser diferent de l\'adreĂ§a electrĂ˛nica personal.','The email is correct'=>'El correu electrĂ˛nic ĂŠs correcte','Remind me later'=>'Recorda-