###SITEURL###','&larr; Go to Categories'=>'&larr; VĂŠs a les categories','Unsupported value type (%s).'=>'Tipus de valor no compatible (%s).','The query does not contain the correct number of placeholders (%1$d) for the number of arguments passed (%2$d).'=>'La consulta no contĂŠ el nombre correcte de textos variables (%1$d) per al nombre d\'arguments que s\'han passat (%2$d).','Your theme can display menus in one location. Select which menu you would like to use.'=>'El tema pot mostrar menĂşs en una ubicaciĂł. Trieu on el voleu utilitzar.','No themes found. Try a different search.'=>'No s\'ha trobat cap tema. Proveu amb una cerca diferent.','menu locationsView Location'=>'Mostra la ubicaciĂł','Looking for a theme? You can search or browse the WordPress.org theme directory, install and preview themes, then activate them right here.'=>'Esteu cercant un tema? Podeu cercar o navegar el directori de temes de WordPress.org, instalÂˇlar i previsualitzar temes, i desprĂŠs, activar-los aquĂ­ mateix.','While previewing a new theme, you can continue to tailor things like widgets and menus, and explore theme-specific options.'=>'Mentre es previsualitza un tema nou, podeu seguir personalitzant elements com ara ginys i menĂşs, i explorar opcions especĂ­fiques del tema.','menu locationsView All Locations'=>'Mostra totes les ubicacions','It does not look like your site has any menus yet. Want to build one? Click the button to start.'=>'Sembla que el lloc web encara no tĂŠ cap menĂş. Voleu crear-ne un? Feu clic al botĂł per a comenĂ§ar.','You&#8217;ll create a menu, assign it a location, and add menu items like links to pages and categories. If your theme has multiple menu areas, you might need to create more than one.'=>'Crea un menĂş, l\'assigna a una ubicaciĂł i afegeix elements de menĂş com ara, per exemple, enllaĂ§os a pĂ gines i categories. Si el tema tĂŠ diverses Ă rees de menĂş, potser haureu de crear-ne mĂŠs d\'una.','menu locationsWhere do you want this menu to appear?'