.','Update anyway, even though it might break your site?'=>'Voleu actualitzar igualment, encara que pugui fer malbĂŠ el web?','%s is already customizing this changeset. Please wait until they are done to try customizing. Your latest changes have been autosaved.'=>'%s ja ha personalitzat aquest conjunt de canvis. Espereu fins que estigui fet per a provar de personalitzar. Els darrers canvis s\'han desat automĂ ticament.','%s is already customizing this changeset. Do you want to take over?'=>'%s estĂ  personalitzant aquest conjunt de canvis ara mateix. Voleu prendre el control?','The link you followed has expired.'=>'L\'enllaĂ§ que heu seguit ha caducat.','WordPress Comments'=>'Comentaris del WordPress','Comment Author'=>'Comentari de l\'autor','Comment Author Email'=>'AdreĂ§a de correu electrĂ˛nic de l\'autor del comentari','Comment Author URL'=>'URL de l\'autor del comentari','You need a higher level of permission.'=>'Necessiteu un nivell mĂŠs alt de permisos.','Comment Author IP'=>'IP de l\'autor del comentari','Comment Author User Agent'=>'Agent d\'usuari de l\'autor del comentari','Comment Date'=>'Data del comentari','Comment Content'=>'Contingut del comentari','Comment URL'=>'URL del comentari','Comment %d contains personal data but could not be anonymized.'=>'El comentari %d contĂŠ dades personals perĂ˛ no s\'ha pogut anonimitzar.','[deleted]'=>'[suprimit]','This content was deleted by the author.'=>'L\'autor ha suprimit aquest contingut.','Privacy Policy'=>'PolĂ­tica de privadesa','Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.'=>'Desa el meu nom, correu electrĂ˛nic i lloc web en aquest navegador per a la prĂ˛xima vegada que comenti.','No archives to show.'=>'No hi ha arxius per a mostrar.','%1$s on %2$s'=>'%1$s a %2$s','No comments to show.'=>'No s\'han trobat comentaris.','Block type names must be strings.'=>'Els noms dels tipus blocs han de ser cadenes de text.','Block type names must not contain uppercase characters.'=>'Els noms dels tipus de bloc no poden contenir carĂ cters en majĂşscula.','Block type names must contain a namespace prefix. Example: my-plugin/my-custom-block-type'=>'Els noms dels blocs han de contenir un prefix com a espai de noms. Per exemple: la-meva-extensio/el-meu-tipus-de-bloc','Block type "%s" is already registered.'=>'El tipus bloc ÂŤ%sÂť ja estĂ  registrat.','Block type "%s" is not registered.'=>'El tipus de bloc ÂŤ%sÂť no estĂ  registrat.','Post published.'=>'S\'ha publicat l\'entrada.','Page published.'=>'S\'ha publicat la pĂ gina.','Post published privately.'=>'S\'ha publicat l\'entrada privadament.','Page published privately.'=>'S\'ha publicat la pĂ gina privadament.','Post reverted to draft.'=>'S\'ha tornat l\'entrada a esborrany.','Page reverted to draft.'=>'S\'ha revertit la pĂ gina a esborrany.','Post scheduled.'=>'S\'ha planificat l\'entrada.','Page scheduled.'=>'S\'ha planificat la pĂ gina.','Post updated.'=>'S\'ha actualitzat l\'entrada.','Page updated.'=>'S\'ha actualitzat la pĂ gina.','%s from now'=>'%s a partir d\'ara','(opens in a new tab)'=>'(s\'obre en una pestanya nova)','Pagination'=>'PaginaciĂł','Classic Block Keyboard Shortcuts'=>'Dreceres de teclat del bloc clĂ ssic','A key value mismatch has been detected. Please follow the link provided in your activation email.'=>'S\'ha detectat un desajust del valor d\'una clau. Seguiu l\'enllaĂ§ que us hem proporcionat en el correu electrĂ˛nic d\'activaciĂł.','A variable mismatch has been detected.'=>'S\'ha detectat un desajust de variable.','This theme failed to load properly and was paused within the admin backend.'=>'Aquest tema no s\'ha pogut carregar correctament i s\'ha aturat al tauler d\'administraciĂł.','%s minute'=>'%s minut' . "\0" . '%s minuts','%s second'=>'%s segon' . "\0" . '%s segons','localized PHP upgrade information pagehttps://wordpress.org/support/update-php/'=>'https://wordpress.org/support/update-php/','This resource is provided by your web host, and is specific to your site. For more information, <a href="%s" target="_blank">see the official WordPress documentation</a>.'=>'Aquest recurs es proporciona per l\'amfitriĂł de la web, i ĂŠs especĂ­fic de la web. Per mĂŠs informaciĂł, <a href="%s" target="_blank">mireu la documentaciĂł oficial del WordPress</a>.','%1$s, %2$s'=>'%1$s, %2$s','Your comment is awaiting moderation. This is a preview; your comment will be visible after it has been approved.'=>'El comentari estĂ  sent moderat. AixĂ˛ ĂŠs una previsualitzaciĂł, el comentari serĂ  visible quan sigui aprovat.','%1$s, and %2$s'=>'%1$s, i %2$s','Update PHP'=>'Actualitzeu el PHP','Quote from Hello Dolly song, by Jerry Herman:'=>'Cita de la canĂ§Ăł Hello Dolly, de Jerry Herman:','%s Comment in moderation'=>'%s comentari en moderaciĂł' . "\0" . '%s comentaris en moderaciĂł','Exit Recovery Mode'=>'Surt del mode recuperaciĂł','https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/advanced-topics/child-themes/'=>'https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/advanced-topics/child-themes/','An error of type %1$s was caused in line %2$s of the file %3$s. Error message: %4$s'=>'Un error del tipus %1$s s\'ha produĂŻt a la lĂ­nia %2$s del fitxer %3$s. El missatge d\'error: %4$s','No cookie present.'=>'No hi ha galeta.','Invalid cookie format.'=>'Format no vĂ lid de galeta.','Cookie expired.'=>'La galeta ha caducat.','Invalid cookie.'=>'Galeta no vĂ lida.','Keep widget settings and move it to the inactive widgets'=>'MantĂŠ la configuraciĂł del giny i mou-lo als ginys inactius','Select Site Icon'=>'Selecciona la icona del lloc','User roleAdministrator'=>'Administrador/a','User roleEditor'=>'Editor/a','User roleAuthor'=>'Autor/a','User roleContributor'=>'ColÂˇlaborador/a','User roleSubscriber'=>'Subscriptor/a','Recovery Mode not initialized.'=>'No s\'ha inicialitzat el mode de recuperaciĂł.','Invalid recovery key format.'=>'Format no vĂ lid de la clau de recuperaciĂł.','Invalid recovery key.'=>'Clau de recuperaciĂł no vĂ lida.','Recovery key expired.'=>'Ha caducat la clau de recuperaciĂł.','Could not update the email last sent time.'=>'No s\'ha pogut actualitzar l\'hora d\'enviament del darrer correu electrĂ˛nic.','The email could not be sent. Possible reason: your host may have disabled the %s function.'=>'No s\'ha pogut enviar el correu electrĂ˛nic. Motiu possible: el servidor pot haver desactivat la funciĂł %s.','A recovery link was already sent %1$s ago. Please wait another %2$s before requesting a new email.'=>'Ja s\'ha enviat un enllaĂ§ de recuperaciĂł fa %1$s. Espereu un altre %2$s abans de solÂˇlicitar un nou correu electrĂ˛nic.','Error Details'=>'Detalls de l\'error','[%s] Your Site is Experiencing a Technical Issue'=>'[%s] El lloc estĂ  experimentat un problema tĂ¨cnic','Error not caused by a plugin or theme.'=>'L\'error no l\'ha causat una extensiĂł o tema.','Failed to store the error.'=>'No s\'ha pogut desar l\'error.','Exit recovery mode link expired.'=>'L\'enllaĂ§ per sortir del mode recuperaciĂł ha caducat.','Failed to exit recovery mode. Please try again later.'=>'No s\'ha pogut sortir del mode de recuperaciĂł. Torneu-ho a provar mĂŠs tard.','[%s] Admin Email Changed'=>'[%s] Ha canviat el correu electrĂ˛nic de l\'administrador','Support'=>'Suport','https://wordpress.org/support/forums/'=>'https://ca.wordpress.org/support/forums/','Error occurred on a non-protected endpoint.'=>'S\'ha produĂŻt un error a un punt final no protegit.','Please contact your host for assistance with investigating this issue further.'=>'Poseu-vos en contacte amb el servidor per obtenir mĂŠs informaciĂł sobre aquesta qĂźestiĂł.','Howdy!

WordPress has a built-in feature that detects when a plugin or theme causes a fatal error on your site, and notifies you with this automated email.
###CAUSE###
First, visit your website (###SITEURL###) and check for any visible issues. Next, visit the page where the error was caught (###PAGEURL###) and check for any visible issues.

###SUPPORT###

If your site appears broken and you can\'t access your dashboard normally, WordPress now has a special "recovery mode". This lets you safely login to your dashboard and investigate further.

###LINK###

To keep your site safe, this link will expire in ###EXPIRES###. Don\'t worry about that, though: a new link will be emailed to you if the error occurs again after it expires.

When seeking help with this issue, you may be asked for some of the following information:
###DEBUG###

###DETAILS###'=>'Hola!

WordPress disposa d\'una funcionalitat integrada que detecta quan una extensiĂł o un tema causa un error fatal al lloc web, i us notifica amb aquest correu electrĂ˛nic automĂ tic.
###CAUSE###
Primer, visiteu la web (###SITEURL###) i comproveu qualsevol problema visible. DesprĂŠs, visiteu la pĂ gina on s\'ha capturat l\'error (###PAGEURL###) i comproveu qualsevol problema visible.

###SUPPORT###

Si el lloc sembla malmĂ¨s i no podeu accedir al tauler normalment, el WordPress tĂŠ ara un ÂŤmode de recuperaciĂłÂť especial. Aquest us deixa iniciar sessiĂł de manera segura al tauler i continuar investigant.

###LINK###

Per mantenir el lloc web segur, aquest enllaĂ§ caduca en ###EXPIRES###. No us preocupeu, per aixĂ˛: un enllaĂ§ nou se us enviarĂ  per correu electrĂ˛nic si l\'error torna a passar desprĂŠs que aquest correu caduqui.

Quan cerqueu informaciĂł sobre aquest problema, se us pot preguntar per alguna de la segĂźent informaciĂł:
