###DETAILS###','In this case, WordPress caught an error with one of your plugins, %s.'=>'En aquest cas, el WordPress ha detectat un error a una de les extensions, %s.','In this case, WordPress caught an error with your theme, %s.'=>'En aquest cas, el WordPress ha detectat un error al tema, %s.','New version available.'=>'Hi ha una nova versiĂł disponible.','Allow people to submit comments on new posts.'=>'Permet a la gent enviar comentaris a les entrades noves.','Cannot resize the image. Both width and height are not set.'=>'No es pot redimensionar la imatge. No s\'han definit ni l\'amplada ni l\'alĂ§ada.','comment_excerpt_length20'=>'20','Original SizeOriginal'=>'Original','excerpt_length55'=>'55','Added:'=>'Afegit:','Unchanged:'=>'Sense canvis:','User&#8217;s comment data.'=>'Dades dels comentaris de l\'usuari.','The image cannot be rotated because the embedded meta data cannot be updated.'=>'No es pot girar la imatge perquĂ¨ les metadades incrustades no es poden actualitzar.','There has been a critical error on this website, putting it in recovery mode. Please check the Themes and Plugins screens for more details. If you just installed or updated a theme or plugin, check the relevant page for that first.'=>'S\'ha produĂŻt un error crĂ­tic a la pĂ gina web, posant-se en mode recuperaciĂł. Comproveu les pantalles dels temes i les extensions per a mĂŠs detalls. Si acabeu d\'instalÂˇlar o actualitzar un tema o extensiĂł, comproveu primer la pĂ gina corresponent.','There has been a critical error on this website.'=>'S\'ha produĂŻt un error crĂ­tic al lloc web.','Block style name must be a string.'=>'El nom d\'estil del bloc ha de ser una cadena de text.','Block "%1$s" does not contain a style named "%2$s".'=>'El bloc ÂŤ%1$sÂť no contĂŠ un estil anomenat ÂŤ%2$sÂť.','Your timezone is set to %1$s (%2$s), currently %3$s (Coordinated Universal Time %4$s).'=>'La zona horĂ ria estĂ  establerta en %1$s (%2$s), actualment %3$s (Temps universal coordinat %4$s).','Your timezo