es should not be run before the %s hook.'=>'Les consultes d\'usuaris no s\'han d\'executar abans del ganxo %s.','https://wordpress.org/documentation/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/','Patterns that contain buttons and call to actions.'=>'Patrons que contenen botons i crides a l\'acciĂł.','Multi-column patterns with more complex layouts.'=>'Patrons de diverses columnes amb dissenys mĂŠs complexos.','Patterns containing mostly text.'=>'Patrons que contenen text principalment.','Display your latest posts in lists, grids or other layouts.'=>'Mostreu les entrades recents a llistes, graelles o altres dissenys.','A set of high quality curated patterns.'=>'Un conjunt de patrons seleccionats d\'alta qualitat.','Block pattern categoryCall to action'=>'Crida a l\'acciĂł','Sections whose purpose is to trigger a specific action.'=>'Seccions que tenen com a finalitat desencadenar una acciĂł concreta.','A variety of designs to display your team members.'=>'Diversos dissenys per a mostrar els membres del vostre equip.','Block pattern categoryTestimonials'=>'Recomanacions','Share reviews and feedback about your brand/business.'=>'Compartiu ressenyes i comentaris sobre la vostra marca/empresa.','Block pattern categoryServices'=>'Serveis','Briefly describe what your business does and how you can help.'=>'Descriviu breument quĂ¨ fa la vostra empresa i com podeu ajudar.','Block pattern categoryContact'=>'Contacte','Display your contact information.'=>'Mostreu la vostra informaciĂł de contacte.','Introduce yourself.'=>'Presenteu-vos.','Block pattern categoryPortfolio'=>'Portfoli','Showcase your latest work.'=>'Mostreu el vostre treball mĂŠs recent.','Different layouts for displaying images.'=>'Diferents dissenys per a mostrar imatges.','Different layouts containing video or audio.'=>'Diferents dissenys que contenen vĂ­deo o Ă udio.','A variety of footer designs displaying information and site navigation.'=>'Diversos dissenys de peu de pĂ gina que mostren informaciĂł i navega